section.div: Favorites genres: Action, Fantasy, Adventure, Drama

div.div:
A catastrophe killed billions of people due to monsters suddenly appearing around the world. Some of the survivors became ‘metahumans’, able to fight against the monsters. This causes a huge divide to form between metahumans and regular humans.
Kim Seon-U is a regular human guide for the metahumans’ beast subjugation. On the verge of death, he hears a voice in his head say: “Kill them. Kill them and take their power!”
(Source: KakaoPage, translated and edited)

In the mysterious, RPG dungeon-like Tower, Confucius Kim lives a mundane existence, envying all the star hunters. One day, his wish for more is granted with a legendary skill to copy others’ abilities… at the cost of his life. Before he can make sense of it, he’s killed by the #1 hunter, the Flame Emperor! But this activates his skill and now he’s copied a new one, the ability to travel back in time upon death. How will Confucius use these skills to outplay the competition and rise to the top?
(Source: Tapas)
